{
  "stem": "8703.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because I didn't know if this was-- you know, among the Polish people, I'm sorry to say, there were collaborators.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Or if they squealed on a Jew, they got a kilo of sugar or a bottle of vodka.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Anyway, I'll go in, and I'll talk to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If you'll see that-- some danger, then it's him or us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And everybody had a knife with them, including me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and I asked him, where-- I want to know, what's the name of this town, of this place that you are?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He told me it wasn't even a-- it was a very small place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the nearest was Bodzentyn, Bodzentyn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How far is it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "About 10, 10-- it was what, 10 kilometers, not miles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said-- he said, you know, if you want to go with me, in a half hour, I'll go with you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Telephones he didn't have, you know, because there, he could have notified us to the police or, or this the [GERMAN] that I am over there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was nice enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He went to the town also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the other two were behind me, watching me, and watching both of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we came a couple of miles, when I saw already the town, I told him, thank you very much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm going a different way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't want to tell him that I am going over there because he went there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he could notify the police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we rented-- and we-- we rented some kind of wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we went home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was the end of that plan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We succeeded very well to escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were very happy [DRINKS] that we escaped from that-- from that camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
